# Homey Teppanyaki Website - Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
Create a one-page branding website for a "Homey Teppanyaki Restaurant" run by a married couple.
The site needs to convey **"Warmth," "Friendliness," and "At-home Atmosphere."**
Design should be inviting, using warm colors to represent the heat of the teppan and the warmth of the service.

## User Review Required
- **Design Vibe**: "Warm & Casual". Orange/Brown tones.
- **Content**: Focus on the couple's hospitality and the sizzling sound of the iron plate.

## Proposed Changes

### Structure
Single page [index.html](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/izakaya_lp/index.html).

#### [NEW] [index.html](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/teppanyaki_lp/index.html)
- **Hero Section**: Close-up of sizzling meat or okonomiyaki on the teppan. Copy: "ジュワッと広がる、笑顔と香り。" (Sizzling smiles and aroma).
- **Concept**: "Husband grills, Wife serves." (夫婦二人三脚). A story of their partnership and love for food.
- **Menu**:
    - Okonomiyaki / Yakisoba
    - Teppan Steak (Wagyu)
    - Iron Plate Side Dishes
- **Atmosphere**: Counter seats where you can talk to the owners.
- **Access**: "Come visit us like you're coming home."

#### [NEW] [style.css](file:///C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/teppanyaki_lp/style.css)
- **Design Concept**: "Sizzle & Smile".
- **Colors**:
    - Primary: Burnt Orange (#D35400) or Warm Red.
    - Background: Beige/Wood texture (#F5DEB3).
    - Text: Dark Brown (#4E342E).
- **Typography**: Rounded Gothic or Handwritten-style fonts for friendliness.

## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
- Check that the design feels "welcoming" and not too high-end/intimidating.
- Verify responsiveness.
